caption.p: The chemical composition of essential oils of the Magnolia grandiflora.

fn.p: RRI: relative retention indices calculated against n-alkanes; %: calculated from FID data; tr: trace (< 0.1 %); IM: identification method based on the relative retention indices (RRI) of authentic compounds on the HP Innowax column; MS, identified based on computer matching of the mass spectra with those of the Wiley and MassFinder libraries and comparison with literature data. % calculated from FID data.; -: not detected.
